I found mine, I'll leave first.

43
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,680
Okay.

44
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:41,860
Bye-bye.

45
00:03:55,050 --> 00:03:57,450
Mom, there's another order.

46
00:03:57,450 --> 00:03:59,690
Have you finished making the previous batch of orders?

47
00:03:59,690 --> 00:04:01,500
