48
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:03,380
The take-out platform will charge us if we're late with the orders.

49
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:06,380
Stop rushing me. Okay, okay, I'm coming.

50
00:04:08,930 --> 00:04:10,490
Have you checked all the addresses?

51
00:04:10,490 --> 00:04:11,710
