57
00:04:27,270 --> 00:04:32,150
If you can't find the address once you're there, just ask around. Okay?

58
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:39,530
It's free if I do it and I do it every time. Look at how tan I am now!

59
00:04:39,530 --> 00:04:42,100
If you don't want to, I'll go.

60
00:04:42,820 --> 00:04:45,110
Or Santu (Xia Yaoyao) could do it, too.

61
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,860
