62
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:53,890
Be quick, okay?

63
00:04:53,890 --> 00:04:55,930
I got it.

64
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,000
Seventeen...

65
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:18,880
Where's Building 18?

66
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:28,910
Hey, Mister. Mister!

67
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:30,490
Uncle may I ask—

68
00:05:30,490 --> 00:05:32,760
Who are you calling uncle?

69
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,960
Why are you here?

70
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:38,470
S-Sorry... I didn't see clearly.

71
00:05:40,470 --> 00:05:42,870
