00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:04,720
Money for rent

183
00:15:11,170 --> 00:15:16,440
I feel like if it's okay, you can come to the Business Center to fill out the form.

184
00:15:25,580 --> 00:15:28,790
Student, are you sure you want to apply for the Architecture Major?
[Fashion Majors]

185
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:31,330
In that case, you can follow us.
[Fashion Major]

186
00:15:31,330 --> 00:15:33,780
What should I pick?
[Fashion Majors]

187
00:15:33,780 --> 00:15:37,160
Fashion Majors

188
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:42,960
It's huge here.

189
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:46,500
This is my first time coming to Haicheng University.

190
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,710
Look how tall that building is.

191
00:15:49,710 --> 00:15:53,480
There are pamphlets for new students over there. Let's take a look.

192
00:15:57,130 --> 00:16:02,350
It's nice being a college student. Look how fashionable they are dressed.

193
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:06,990
Hello, thank you.

194
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:15,260
My Journalism Major is over there. Let's go look.

195
00:16:18,430 --> 00:16:20,640
- Architecture Majors

196
00:16:22,380 --> 00:16:23,980
This...

